script-properties.script.text:
' Global Namespace ' Utilities functions ''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''' Function QuoteStr(Str, Quote) If Quote Then QuoteStr = """" & Str & """" Else QuoteStr = Str End If End Function
Function QuoteStrEx(Str, Quote, StartQuote, EndQuote) If Quote Then QuoteStrEx = StartQuote & Str & EndQuote Else QuoteStrEx = Str End If End Function
Function Tabs(NumTabs) Dim i For i = 1 To NumTabs Tabs = Tabs & vbTab Next End Function
Function QuoteStrE(Str, Context) Quote = Context.Options.Property("Quote Names").AsBoolean Or Context.NameShouldBeQuoted(Str) If Quote Then QuoteStrE = """" & Str & """" Else QuoteStrE = Str End If End Function
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''' Function ObjectName(ObjectInstance, Options) ObjectName = "" Quote = Options.Property("Quote Names").AsBoolean Or ObjectInstance.NameShouldBeQuoted() If ObjectInstance.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then ObjectName = QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.Property("Schema").AsString, Quote) & "." End If ObjectName = ObjectName & QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.Property("Name").AsString, Quote) End Function
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''' Function ObjectNameEx(ObjectInstance, Options, Quote, StartQuote, EndQuote) ObjectNameEx = "" Quote = Quote Or ObjectInstance.NameShouldBeQuoted() If ObjectInstance.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then ObjectNameEx = QuoteStrEx(ObjectInstance.Property("Schema").AsString, Quote, StartQuote, EndQuote) & "." End If ObjectNameEx = ObjectNameEx & QuoteStrEx(ObjectInstance.Property("Name").AsString, Quote, StartQuote, EndQuote) End Function
''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
Function ObjectOriginalName(ObjectInstance, Options) ObjectOriginalName = "" Quote = Options.Property("Quote Names").AsBoolean Or ObjectInstance.NameShouldBeQuoted() If ObjectInstance.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then ObjectOriginalName = QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.OriginalProperty("Schema").AsString, Quote) & "." End If ObjectOriginalName = ObjectOriginalName & QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString, Quote) End Function
''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
' extend the list as required... Function IsReservedWord(Name) IsReservedWord = (UCase(Name) = "LEVEL" Or UCase(Name) = "EXTERNAL" Or UCase(Name) = "DATABASE") End Function
Function QualifiedName(ObjectInstance, TilOwner, Quote) Dim Owner Dim OwnerName Set Owner = ObjectInstance.Owner() Dim Name Name = ObjectInstance.Name Dim NameQuote NameQuote = Quote If Not NameQuote Then NameQuote = IsReservedWord(Name) End If If Owner.Equals(TilOwner) = False Then OwnerName = QualifiedName(Owner, TilOwner, Quote) If OwnerName <> "" Then OwnerName = OwnerName & "." End If QualifiedName = OwnerName & QuoteStr(Name, NameQuote) Exit Function End If QualifiedName = QuoteStr(Name, NameQuote) End Function
Function QualifiedNameEx(ObjectInstance, TilOwner, Quote, QuoteStart, QuoteEnd) Dim Owner Dim OwnerName Set Owner = ObjectInstance.Owner() Dim Name Name = ObjectInstance.Name Dim NameQuote NameQuote = Quote If Not NameQuote Then NameQuote = IsReservedWord(Name) End If If Owner.Equals(TilOwner) = False Then OwnerName = QualifiedNameEx(Owner, TilOwner, Quote, QuoteStart, QuoteEnd) If OwnerName <> "" Then OwnerName = OwnerName & "." End If QualifiedNameEx = OwnerName & QuoteStrEx(Name, NameQuote, QuoteStart, QuoteEnd) Exit Function End If QualifiedNameEx = QuoteStrEx(Name, NameQuote, QuoteStart, QuoteEnd) End Function
Sub OutputObjectName(ObjectInstance, Doc, Options) Quote = Options.Property("Quote Names").AsBoolean Or ObjectInstance.NameShouldBeQuoted() If ObjectInstance.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Doc.Write(QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.Property("Schema").AsString, Quote) & ".") End If Doc.Write(QuoteStr(ObjectInstance.Property("Name").AsString, Quote)) End Sub
Function ObjectHeader(ObjectInstance, Options) If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Dim ObjectName ObjectName = ObjectInstance.Property("Name").AsString Dim ObjectTypeName ObjectTypeName = ObjectInstance.TypeName ObjectHeader = "--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE " & UCase(ObjectTypeName) & ": " & ObjectName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine End If End Function
Function ProcessFKConstraintInModelSubset(Relation) Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options ProcessFKConstraintInModelSubset = True If Options.Property("Generate FK Model Subset Only").AsBoolean Then If Context.HasSelectedModelSubset And Context.ContainedInSelectedModelSubset(Relation) = False Then ProcessFKConstraintInModelSubset = False End If End If End Function
Function GenerateName(Obj) GenerateName = True If Obj.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then GenerateName = False End If End Function
Function IsNewObject(Obj) Dim Owner Set Owner = Obj.Owner() Dim ObjTypeName ObjTypeName = Obj.TypeName Set Children = Owner.OriginalChildren(ObjTypeName) For Each Child In Children If Child.Id = Obj.Id Then IsNewObject = False Exit Function End If Next IsNewObject = True End Function
Function ChildByName(OwnerObj, ChildTypeName, ChildName) Set Children = OwnerObj.Children(ChildTypeName) For Each Child In Children If Child.Name = ChildName Then Set ChildByName = Child Exit Function End If Next End Function
Function column_default_expr(Column, Options) If Column.Property("Default Expression").AsString <> "" Then column_default_expr = "DEFAULT " column_default_expr = column_default_expr & Column.Property("Default Expression").AsString End If End Function
Function IsViewConstraint(Constraint) IsViewConstraint = False If Constraint.Owner.TypeName = "View" or Constraint.Owner.TypeName = "Materialized View" Then IsViewConstraint = True ElseIf Constraint.Owner.Owner.TypeName = "View" or Constraint.Owner.Owner.TypeName = "Materialized View" Then IsViewConstraint = True End If End Function
Function OracleConstraintState(Constraint) OracleConstraintState = "" If Constraint.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then ' Generate Constraint State If Constraint.HasProperty("Deferrable") Then If Constraint.Property("Deferrable").AsBoolean Then OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " DEFERRABLE" Else OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " NOT DEFERRABLE" End If End If If Constraint.HasProperty("Deferred") Then If Constraint.Property("Deferred").AsBoolean Then OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " INITIALLY DEFERRED" Else OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " INITIALLY IMMEDIATE" End If End If If IsViewConstraint(Constraint) Then OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " DISABLE" ElseIf Constraint.HasProperty("Enable") Then If Constraint.Property("Enable").AsBoolean Then OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " ENABLE" Else OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " DISABLE" End If End If If Constraint.HasProperty("Validate") Then If Constraint.Property("Validate").AsBoolean Then OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " VALIDATE" Else OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " NOVALIDATE" End If End If ' RELY/NORELY applies only to existing constraints! ' If Constraint.HasProperty("Rely") Then ' If Constraint.Property("Rely").AsBoolean Then ' OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " RELY" ' Else ' OracleConstraintState = OracleConstraintState & " NORELY" ' End If ' End If End If End Function
Function PostgresqlConstraintState(Constraint) PostgresqlConstraintState = "" If Constraint.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then ' Generate Constraint State If Constraint.HasProperty("Deferrable") Then If PostgresqlConstraintState <> "" Then PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & " " End If If Constraint.Property("Deferrable").AsBoolean Then PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & "DEFERRABLE" Else PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & "NOT DEFERRABLE" End If End If If Constraint.HasProperty("Deferred") Then If PostgresqlConstraintState <> "" Then PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & " " End If If Constraint.Property("Deferred").AsBoolean Then PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & "INITIALLY DEFERRED" Else PostgresqlConstraintState = PostgresqlConstraintState & "INITIALLY IMMEDIATE" End If End If End If End Function
Function Delim(Options) Delim = Options.Property("Delim").AsString Delim = Replace(Delim, "\n", vbNewLine) Delim = Replace(Delim, "\t", vbTab) End Function
Sub AddDelim(Options, Document) Document.Write(Delim(Options)) End Sub
Function ProgDelim(Options) ProgDelim = Options.Property("Prog Delim").AsString ProgDelim = Replace(ProgDelim, "\n", vbNewLine) ProgDelim = Replace(ProgDelim, "\t", vbTab) End Function
Sub AddProgDelim(Options, Document) Document.Write(ProgDelim(Options)) End Sub
Function DatatypeName(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then DatatypeName = Left(Datatype, Idx - 1) Else DatatypeName = Datatype End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam1(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Idx2 - Idx - 1) Else DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx - 1) End If End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam2(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam2 = Mid(Datatype, Idx2 + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx2 - 1) End If End If End Function
Function OriginalObjectName(Obj) If Obj.HasOriginalProperty("Name") = True Then OriginalObjectName = Obj.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit Function End If OriginalObjectName = Obj.Property("Name").AsString End Function
Function AlteredBoolProp(Obj, ModifiedProps, Prop, TrueStr, FalseStr, DefaultStr) If Not ModifiedProps.HasProperty(Prop) Then Exit Function End If If Obj.HasOriginalProperty(Prop) Then If Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then ' prop in both places If Obj.Property(Prop).AsString <> Obj.OriginalProperty(Prop).AsString Then If Obj.Property(Prop).AsBoolean Then AlteredBoolProp = AlteredBoolProp & TrueStr Else AlteredBoolProp = AlteredBoolProp & FalseStr End If End If Else ' prop was removed If Obj.OriginalProperty(Prop).AsBoolean And DefaultStr <> "" Then AlteredBoolProp = AlteredBoolProp & DefaultStr End If End If ElseIf Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then If Obj.Property(Prop).AsBoolean Then AlteredBoolProp = AlteredBoolProp & TrueStr Else AlteredBoolProp = AlteredBoolProp & FalseStr End If End If End Function
Function AlteredProp(Obj, ModifiedProps, Prop, PrefixStr, PostStr, DefaultStr) If Not ModifiedProps.HasProperty(Prop) Then Exit Function End If If Obj.HasOriginalProperty(Prop) Then If Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then ' prop in both places If Obj.Property(Prop).AsString <> Obj.OriginalProperty(Prop).AsString Then AlteredProp = AlteredProp & PrefixStr & Obj.Property(Prop).AsString & PostStr End If Else ' prop was removed AlteredProp = AlteredProp & DefaultStr End If ElseIf Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then AlteredProp = AlteredProp & PrefixStr & Obj.Property(Prop).AsString & PostStr End If End Function
Function AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal(Obj, ModifiedProps, Prop, PrefixStr, SpecialStr, SpecialVal, DefaultStr) If Not ModifiedProps.HasProperty(Prop) Then Exit Function End If If Obj.HasOriginalProperty(Prop) Then If Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then ' prop in both places If Obj.Property(Prop).AsString <> Obj.OriginalProperty(Prop).AsString Then If Obj.Property(Prop).AsInteger = SpecialVal Then AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal = AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal & SpecialStr Else AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal = AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal & PrefixStr & Obj.Property(Prop).AsString End If End If Else ' prop was removed AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal = AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal & DefaultStr End If ElseIf Obj.HasProperty(Prop) Then If Obj.Property(Prop).AsInteger = SpecialVal Then AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal = AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal & SpecialStr Else AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal = AlteredIntPropWithSpecialVal & PrefixStr & Obj.Property(Prop).AsString End If End If End Function
Function TableOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TableOwner = Nothing Exit Function End If If Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" Then Set TableOwner = Obj Else Set TableOwner = TableOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function

script-properties.script.name: Drop Temporary Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Temporary Table Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Table Set Table = Context.Object If Table.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString TemporaryTableName = "MR_TEMP_" & TableName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP TEMPORARY TABLE: " & TemporaryTableName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TABLE IF EXISTS ") If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TemporaryTableName, Context) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Rename To Temporary Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Copy Table to Temporary Table Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Table Set Table = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim ModifiedProperty OriginalTableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString TemporaryTableName = "MR_TEMP_" & OriginalTableName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- COPY TO TEMPORARY TABLE: " & OriginalTableName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalTableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(OriginalTableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(TemporaryTableName, Context)) AddDelim Options, Document End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Insert Data Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Insert Data From Temporary Table Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Table Set Table = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString TemporaryTableName = "MR_TEMP_" & TableName If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- INSERT DATA FROM TEMPORARY TABLE: " & TemporaryTableName & " -> " & TableName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Dim OriginalColumns Set OriginalColumns = Table.OriginalChildren("Column") Dim CurrentColumns Set CurrentColumns = Table.Children("Column") ' Build list of columns.... Dim CurrentColumnsString Dim OriginalColumnsString For Each Column In CurrentColumns Dim ColumnName ColumnName = Column.Property("Name").AsString Dim OriginalColumnValue Dim ColumnFound ColumnFound = False For Each OriginalColumn In OriginalColumns If OriginalColumn.Property("Name").AsString = ColumnName Then ColumnFound = True OriginalColumnValue = OriginalObjectName(OriginalColumn) Exit For End If Next If ColumnFound = False Then OriginalColumnValue = Column.Property("Insert Value For Column").AsString End If If OriginalColumnValue <> "" Then If CurrentColumnsString = "" Then CurrentColumnsString = ColumnName Else CurrentColumnsString = CurrentColumnsString & ", " & ColumnName End If If OriginalColumnsString = "" Then OriginalColumnsString = OriginalColumnValue Else OriginalColumnsString = OriginalColumnsString & ", " & OriginalColumnValue End If ElseIf Column.Property("Not Null").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--- TO DO: NO SUITABLE DEFAULT VALUE GENERATE FOR COLUMN " & ColumnName & "; PLEASE REVIEW SCRIPT FOR MANUAL CHANGES" & vbNewLine) End If Next If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("INSERT INTO " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("INSERT INTO " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If Document.Write("(" & CurrentColumnsString & ")" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("SELECT " & OriginalColumnsString & vbNewLine) If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("FROM " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TemporaryTableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("FROM " & QuoteStrE(TemporaryTableName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Convert Datatype
script-properties.script.text:
' Convert to PostgreSQL Datatype Function DatatypeName(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then DatatypeName = Left(Datatype, Idx - 1) Else DatatypeName = Datatype End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam1(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Idx2 - Idx - 1) Else DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx - 1) End If Else DatatypeParam1 = -1 End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam2(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam2 = Mid(Datatype, Idx2 + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx2 - 1) Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Obj Set Obj = Context.Object Dim PrevDatabase PrevDatabase = Context.PrevDatabase Dim CurDatatype CurDatatype = Obj.Property("Datatype").AsString Dim CurName CurName = DatatypeName(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam1 CurParam1 = DatatypeParam1(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam2 CurParam2 = DatatypeParam2(CurDatatype) Dim NewDatatype NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Select Case PrevDatabase Case "MySQL 5.0", "MySQL 5.1", "MySQL 6.0" Select Case CurName Case "BIT", "BOOL", "BOOLEAN" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "TINYINT", "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "MEDIUMINT", "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "DEC", "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC", "FIXED" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "DATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "YEAR" NewDatatype = "date" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR", "CHARACTER VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR", "NATIONAL CHARACTER VARYING", "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "BINARY", "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bit varying" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "MEDIUMBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "LONGBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "TINYTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "TEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "MEDIUMTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "LONGTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "ENUM" NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Case "SET" NewDatatype = "varchar(100)" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "Oracle 8i", "Oracle 9i", "Oracle 10g", "Oracle 11g" Select Case CurName Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "NUMBER" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE", "TIMESTAMP WITH LOCAL TIME ZONE" NewDatatype = "timestamp with time zone" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR2", "CHARACTER VARYING", "CHAR VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "RAW" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "NCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the datatype get deleted - will inherit the default End Select Case "SQL Server 2000", "SQL Server 2005", "SQL Server 2008", "SQL Azure", "SQL Server Compact 3.5" Select Case CurName Case "bigint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "int" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "smallint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "tinyint" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "bit" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "decimal", "numeric" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "money" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "smallmoney" NewDatatype = "money" Case "float" NewDatatype = "real" Case "real" NewDatatype = "real" Case "datetime", "smalldatetime", "datetime2", "datetimeoffset" NewDatatype = "date" Case "timestamp" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "time" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "date" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "char" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "varchar" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "text", "ntext" NewDatatype = "text" Case "nchar" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "nvarchar" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "binary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "varbinary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "image" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "sql_variant" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "rowversion" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "uniqueidentifier" NewDatatype = "integer" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "ODBC", "Access 2003", "Access 2007", "Access 2010" Select Case CurName Case "BIT" NewDatatype = "boolean" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATETIME", "UTCDATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME", "UTCTIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "WCHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "BINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "GUID" NewDatatype = "char(128)" Case "UNKNOWN" NewDatatype = "" Case Else NewDatatype = "" End Select Case "DB2 LUW 7", "DB2 UDB 8", "DB2 LUW 9", "DB2 LUW 9.5", "DB2 LUW 9.7", "DB2 7 for z/OS", "DB2 8 for z/OS", "DB2 9 for z/OS" Select Case CurName Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "BLOB", "BINARY LARGE OBJECT" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CHAR", "CHARACTER" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If End If Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECFLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "INTEGER", "INT" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then If CurParam1 <= 8000 Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If End If End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If Case "GRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "LONG VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "DBCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DB2SECURITYLABEL" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "XML" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case Else Document.Write("Unknown Previous Database") Exit Sub End Select If NewDatatype <> "" Then Obj.SetDatatype(NewDatatype) End If Document.Write("Ok") End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Create Table Script Function constraint_definitions(Table, Options, NumTabs) Dim Clause
Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext")
' PK Constraint If Options.Property("Generate PK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate PK With Alter").AsBoolean = False And Table.HasProperty("Primary Key") Then Dim PrimaryKey Set PrimaryKey = Table.Property("Primary Key").AsObject If Context.IsSelectedObject(PrimaryKey) = True Then Clause = PrimaryKey.Evaluate("Details Script") If Clause <> "" Then If constraint_definitions <> "" Then constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & "," & vbNewLine End If constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & Tabs(NumTabs) & Clause End If ' Clause <> "" End If End If ' Options.Property("Generate PK").AsBoolean = True If Options.Property("Generate UK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate UK With Alter").AsBoolean = False Then Dim UkConstraint For Each UkConstraint In Table.Children("Key Constraint") If UkConstraint.Property("Type").AsString = "Unique" And Context.IsSelectedObject(UkConstraint) = True Then Clause = UkConstraint.Evaluate("Details Script") If Clause <> "" Then If constraint_definitions <> "" Then constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & "," & vbNewLine End If constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & Tabs(NumTabs) & Clause End If ' Clause <> "" End If Next End If If Options.Property("Generate FK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate FK With Alter").AsBoolean = False Then ' FK Constraints Dim Relation For Each Relation In Table.Children("Relation") If ProcessFKConstraintInModelSubset(Relation) = True And Context.IsSelectedObject(Relation) = True Then Clause = Relation.Evaluate("Details Script") If Clause <> "" Then If constraint_definitions <> "" Then constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & "," & vbNewLine End If constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & Tabs(NumTabs) & Clause End If End If Next End If ' Check Constraints Dim CheckConstraint For Each CheckConstraint In Table.Children("Check Constraint") If CheckConstraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Clause = "CONSTRAINT " & ObjectName(CheckConstraint, Context.Options) & " " End If Clause = Clause & "CHECK (" & CheckConstraint.Evaluate("Search Condition") & ")" Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(CheckConstraint) If State <> "" Then Clause = Clause & " " & State End If If Clause <> "" Then If constraint_definitions <> "" Then constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & "," & vbNewLine End If constraint_definitions = constraint_definitions & Tabs(NumTabs) & Clause End If Next End Function
Function column_definitions(Table) ' Columns Dim First Dim Column Dim Columns Dim Clause
First = True Set Columns = Table.Children("Column") For Each Column In Columns Clause = Column.Evaluate("Details Script") If Clause <> "" Then If First = False Then column_definitions = column_definitions & "," & vbNewLine Else First = False End If column_definitions = column_definitions & vbTab & Clause End If Next End Function
Function create_definition(Table, Options) ' Columns Dim Clause
create_definition = column_definitions(Table) Clause = constraint_definitions(Table, Options, 1) If Clause <> "" Then create_definition = create_definition & "," & vbNewLine & Clause End If End Function
Function table_option(Table, Options) Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim StorageParam If Table.HasProperty("Fill Factor") Then StorageParam = "Fillfactor=" & Table.Property("Fill Factor").AsString End If If Table.HasProperty("OIDS") Then If StorageParam <> "" Then StorageParam = StorageParam & ", " End If If Table.Property("OIDS").AsBoolean Then StorageParam = StorageParam & "OIDS=TRUE" Else StorageParam = StorageParam & "OIDS=FALSE" End If End If If StorageParam <> "" Then table_option = table_option & vbNewLine & "WITH (" & StorageParam & ")" End If If Table.HasProperty("TABLESPACE") Then table_option = table_option & vbNewLine & "TABLESPACE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("TABLESPACE").AsString, Context) End If End Function
Function create_table_stmt(Table, Options, NumTabs) If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & ObjectHeader(Table, Options) End If create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & "CREATE" If Table.HasProperty("Temporary") Then If Table.Property("Temporary").AsString = "Session" Then create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & " TEMPORARY" End If End If create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & " TABLE " create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & ObjectName(Table, Options)
Dim Clause Clause = create_definition(Table, Options) If Clause <> "" Then create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & vbNewLine & "(" & vbNewLine & Clause & vbNewLine & ")" End If
Clause = table_option(Table, Options) If Clause <> "" Then create_table_stmt = create_table_stmt & Clause End If
End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim CreateStmt ' holds the value for any sub-object's create stmt string Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Table Set Table = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Column Dim Columns Dim Index Dim Indexes Dim Trigger Dim Triggers Dim PrimaryKey Dim Relation Dim UkConstraint Dim CheckConstraint Dim TableType Dim ColType ' Generate the Table If Options.Property("Create Tables").AsBoolean = False Or Table.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If
Dim AnyColumns AnyColumns = False Set Columns = Table.Children("Column") ' See if there are any columns that are set to generate For Each Column In Columns If Column.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then AnyColumns = True Exit For End If Next If AnyColumns = False Then Exit Sub End If ' Any Columns
Document.Write(create_table_stmt(Table, Options, 1))
' Done Table Options AddDelim Options, Document
' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Table.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON TABLE " & ObjectName(Table, Options) & " IS '" & Table.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If For Each Column In Table.Children("Column") If Column.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If Column.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON COLUMN ") Document.Write(ObjectName(Table, Options) & "." & QuoteStrE(Column.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" IS '" & Column.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If Next End If ' End Generate Comments If Table.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER TABLE " & ObjectName(Table, Options) & " OWNER TO " & Table.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If
' Done Table ' Alter Key Constraints Dim AlterStmt If Options.Property("Generate PK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate PK With Alter").AsBoolean = True And Table.HasProperty("Primary Key") Then Set PrimaryKey = Table.Property("Primary Key").AsObject If Context.IsSelectedObject(PrimaryKey) = True Then AlterStmt = PrimaryKey.Evaluate("Create Script") If AlterStmt <> "" Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = PrimaryKey.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & AlterStmt & vbNewLine) If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = PrimaryKey.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If End If If Options.Property("Generate UK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate UK With Alter").AsBoolean Then For Each UkConstraint In Table.ChildrenSortedByName("Key Constraint") If UkConstraint.Property("Type").AsString = "Unique" and Context.IsSelectedObject(UkConstraint) = True Then AlterStmt = UkConstraint.Evaluate("Create Script") If AlterStmt <> "" Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = UkConstraint.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & AlterStmt & vbNewLine) If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = UkConstraint.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If Next End If ' Generate Indexes If Options.Property("Create Indexes").AsBoolean Then Set Indexes = Table.ChildrenSortedByName("Index") For Each Index In Indexes If Context.IsSelectedObject(Index) = True Then CreateStmt = Index.Evaluate("Create Script") If CreateStmt <> "" Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Index.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & CreateStmt) If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Index.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If Next End If ' End Generate Indexes If Options.Property("Generate FK").AsBoolean = True And Options.Property("Generate FK With Alter").AsBoolean Then ' FK Constraints Dim FKConstraints Set FKConstraints = Table.ChildrenSortedByName("Relation") Dim FKConstraint For Each FKConstraint In FKConstraints If ProcessFKConstraintInModelSubset(FKConstraint) = True and Context.IsSelectedObject(FKConstraint) = True Then AlterStmt = FKConstraint.Evaluate("Create Script") If AlterStmt <> "" Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = FKConstraint.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & AlterStmt & vbNewLine) If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = FKConstraint.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If Next End If Set Sequences = Table.Model.AsObject.ChildrenSortedByName("PGSQL Sequence") For Each Sequence In Sequences If Sequence.HasProperty("Owned By") Then Dim SeqColumn Set SeqColumn = Sequence.Property("Owned By").AsObject Dim SeqTable Set SeqTable = SeqColumn.Owner If Table.Id() = SeqTable.Id() Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Sequence.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options) & " OWNED BY " & ObjectName(Table, Options) & "." & SeqColumn.Property("Name").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Sequence.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If Next ' Generate Triggers If Options.Property("Create Triggers").AsBoolean Then Set Triggers = Table.Children("Trigger") For Each Trigger In Triggers If Context.IsSelectedObject(Trigger) And Not Trigger.Property("Generate At End").AsBoolean Then CreateStmt = Trigger.Evaluate("Create Script") If CreateStmt <> "" Then If Options.Property("Generate Pre Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Trigger.Evaluate("Pre Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & CreateStmt) If Options.Property("Generate Post Scripts").AsBoolean Then PScript = Trigger.Evaluate("Post Script") If PScript <> "" Then Document.Write(PScript) End If End If End If End If Next End If ' End Generate Triggers End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter Table Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Table Set Table = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim ModifiedProperty CurrentTableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString ' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In Table.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalTableName = Table.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER TABLE: " & OriginalTableName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalTableName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentTableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(OriginalTableName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentTableName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next BaseAlterStr = "--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER TABLE: " & CurrentTableName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then BaseAlterStr = AlterStr & "ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.OriginalProperty("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentTableName, Context) & " " Else BaseAlterStr = AlterStr & Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(CurrentTableName, Context)) & " " End If For Each ModifiedProperty In Table.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Fill Factor" Then Document.Write(BaseAlterStr) If Table.HasProperty("Fill Factor") Then Document.Write("SET (Fillfactor=" & Table.Property("Fill Factor").AsString & ")") Else Document.Write("RESET (Fillfactor)") End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "OIDS" Then If Table.Property("OIDS").AsBoolean = False Then Document.Write(BaseAlterStr) Document.Write("SET WITHOUT OIDS") AddDelim Options, Document End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "TABLESPACE" Then If Table.HasProperty("TABLESPACE") = True Then Document.Write(BaseAlterStr) Document.Write("SET TABLESPACE " & Table.Property("TABLESPACE").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write(BaseAlterStr) Document.Write("SET SCHEMA " & Table.Property("Schema").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If Table.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write(BaseAlterStr) Document.Write("OWNER TO " & Table.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON TABLE " & ObjectName(Table, Options) & " IS '" & Table.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Details Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Create Column Script
Function inline_constraint(Column, Options) inline_constraint = "" Dim Generate Dim CheckConstraints Dim CheckConstraint Dim ConstraintClause Set CheckConstraints = Column.Children("Check Constraint") For Each CheckConstraint In CheckConstraints Generate = True ' Generate Not Null only if the name can be generated... If CheckConstraint.Property("Type").AsString = "NotNull" Then If CheckConstraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If End If If CheckConstraint.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If If Generate = True Then If CheckConstraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then ConstraintClause = "CONSTRAINT " & ObjectName(CheckConstraint, Options) & " " End If ConstraintClause = ConstraintClause & "CHECK (" & CheckConstraint.Evaluate("Search Condition") & ")" Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(CheckConstraint) If State <> "" Then ConstraintClause = ConstraintClause & " " & State End If If ConstraintClause <> "" Then If inline_constraint <> "" Then inline_constraint = inline_constraint + " " End If inline_constraint = inline_constraint + ConstraintClause End If End If Next End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Column Set Column = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Clause If Column.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If Document.Write(ObjectName(Column, Context.Options)) Document.Write(" ") Dim DbDomainObj Dim DbDomain Dim ColType Dim TypeDims If Column.Property("DB Domain").IsNull = False Then Set DbDomainObj = Column.Property("DB Domain").AsObject DbDomain = DbDomainObj.Property("Name").AsString Document.Write(DbDomain) Else ColType = Column.Property("Datatype").AsString Document.Write(ColType) If Column.HasProperty("Dimensions") Then Document.Write(Column.Property("Dimensions").AsString) End If End If ' don't generate default value for serial & bigserial If ColType <> "serial" and ColType <> "bigserial" Then Clause = column_default_expr(Column, Options) If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If End If If Column.HasProperty("Not Null") And Column.Property("Not Null").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" " & Column.Property("Not Null").AsString) End If Clause = inline_constraint(Column, Options) If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Create Column Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE COLUMN: " & CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Dim TableObject Set TableObject = CurrentObject.Owner Dim TableName TableName = CurrentObject.Owner.Property("Name").AsString If TableObject.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableObject.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If ColumnBody = CurrentObject.Evaluate("Details Script") Document.Write(" ADD COLUMN " & ColumnBody ) AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If CurrentObject.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON COLUMN ") Document.Write(ObjectName(TableObject, Options) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" IS '" & CurrentObject.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Column Script
Function column_datatype(Column) Dim DbDomainObj Dim TypeDims If Column.Property("DB Domain").IsNull = False Then Set DbDomainObj = Column.Property("DB Domain").AsObject column_datatype = DbDomainObj.Property("Name").AsString Else column_datatype = Column.Property("Datatype").AsString If Column.HasProperty("Dimensions") Then column_datatype = column_datatype & Column.Property("Dimensions").AsString End If End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Column Set Column = Context.Object Dim Table Set Table = Column.Owner Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim ModifiedProperty ' Generate alteration in order ... Dim ModifedProps Set ModifedProps = Column.ModifiedProperties ' Generate Name first TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalColumnName = Column.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString CurrentColumnName = Column.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- COLUMN RENAME: " & OriginalColumnName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME COLUMN " & QuoteStrE(OriginalColumnName, Context) & " TO " & CurrentColumnName) AddDelim Options, Document End If Next
Dim AlterColumnClause ColumnName = Column.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeAltered TypeAltered = False For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Default Expression" Then If AlterColumnClause <> "" Then AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & ", " End If AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " ALTER " & QuoteStrE(ColumnName, Context) If Column.HasProperty("Default Expression") Then AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " SET " & column_default_expr(Column, Options) Else AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " DROP DEFAULT" End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Datatype" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Datatype Length" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Datatype Precision" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Datatype Scale" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "DB Domain" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Dimensions" Then If TypeAltered = False Then If AlterColumnClause <> "" Then AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & ", " End If AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " ALTER " & QuoteStrE(ColumnName, Context) AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " TYPE " & column_datatype(Column) TypeAltered = True End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Not Null" Then If AlterColumnClause <> "" Then AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & ", " End If AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " ALTER " & QuoteStrE(ColumnName, Context) If Column.HasProperty("Not Null") And Column.Property("Not Null").AsBoolean Then AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " SET NOT NULL" Else AlterColumnClause = AlterColumnClause & " DROP NOT NULL" End If End If Next
If AlterColumnClause <> "" Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER COLUMN: " & ColumnName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(AlterColumnClause) AddDelim Options, Document End If
' Comment... For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- COLUMN COMMENT CHANGE: " & ColumnName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("COMMENT ON COLUMN ") Document.Write(ObjectName(Table, Options) & "." & QuoteStrE(Column.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" IS '" & Column.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next
End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Column Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim TableObject Set TableObject = CurrentObject.Owner Dim TableName TableName = CurrentObject.Owner.Property("Name").AsString ColumnName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP COLUMN: " & TableName & "." & ColumnName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & ObjectName(TableObject, Options)) Document.Write(" DROP COLUMN " & QuoteStrE(ColumnName, Context) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Convert Datatype
script-properties.script.text:
' Convert to PostgreSQL Datatype Function DatatypeName(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then DatatypeName = Left(Datatype, Idx - 1) Else DatatypeName = Datatype End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam1(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Idx2 - Idx - 1) Else DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx - 1) End If Else DatatypeParam1 = -1 End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam2(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam2 = Mid(Datatype, Idx2 + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx2 - 1) Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Obj Set Obj = Context.Object Dim PrevDatabase PrevDatabase = Context.PrevDatabase Dim CurDatatype CurDatatype = Obj.Property("Datatype").AsString Dim CurName CurName = DatatypeName(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam1 CurParam1 = DatatypeParam1(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam2 CurParam2 = DatatypeParam2(CurDatatype) Dim NewDatatype NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Select Case PrevDatabase Case "MySQL 5.0", "MySQL 5.1", "MySQL 6.0" Select Case CurName Case "BIT", "BOOL", "BOOLEAN" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "TINYINT", "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "MEDIUMINT", "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "DEC", "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC", "FIXED" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "DATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "YEAR" NewDatatype = "date" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR", "CHARACTER VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR", "NATIONAL CHARACTER VARYING", "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "BINARY", "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bit varying" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "MEDIUMBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "LONGBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "TINYTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "TEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "MEDIUMTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "LONGTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "ENUM" NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Case "SET" NewDatatype = "varchar(100)" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "Oracle 8i", "Oracle 9i", "Oracle 10g", "Oracle 11g" Select Case CurName Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "NUMBER" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE", "TIMESTAMP WITH LOCAL TIME ZONE" NewDatatype = "timestamp with time zone" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR2", "CHARACTER VARYING", "CHAR VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "RAW" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "NCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the datatype get deleted - will inherit the default End Select Case "SQL Server 2000", "SQL Server 2005", "SQL Server 2008", "SQL Azure", "SQL Server Compact 3.5" Select Case CurName Case "bigint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "int" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "smallint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "tinyint" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "bit" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "decimal", "numeric" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "money" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "smallmoney" NewDatatype = "money" Case "float" NewDatatype = "real" Case "real" NewDatatype = "real" Case "datetime", "smalldatetime", "datetime2", "datetimeoffset" NewDatatype = "date" Case "timestamp" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "time" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "date" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "char" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "varchar" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "text", "ntext" NewDatatype = "text" Case "nchar" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "nvarchar" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "binary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "varbinary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "image" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "sql_variant" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "rowversion" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "uniqueidentifier" NewDatatype = "integer" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "ODBC", "Access 2003", "Access 2007", "Access 2010" Select Case CurName Case "BIT" NewDatatype = "boolean" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATETIME", "UTCDATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME", "UTCTIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "WCHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "BINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "GUID" NewDatatype = "char(128)" Case "UNKNOWN" NewDatatype = "" Case Else NewDatatype = "" End Select Case "DB2 LUW 7", "DB2 UDB 8", "DB2 LUW 9", "DB2 LUW 9.5", "DB2 LUW 9.7", "DB2 7 for z/OS", "DB2 8 for z/OS", "DB2 9 for z/OS" Select Case CurName Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "BLOB", "BINARY LARGE OBJECT" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CHAR", "CHARACTER" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If End If Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECFLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "INTEGER", "INT" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then If CurParam1 <= 8000 Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If End If End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If Case "GRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "LONG VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "DBCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DB2SECURITYLABEL" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "XML" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case Else Document.Write("Unknown Previous Database") Exit Sub End Select If NewDatatype <> "" Then Obj.SetDatatype(NewDatatype) End If Document.Write("Ok") End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Create Schema Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Schema Set Schema = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options If Schema.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim SchemaName SchemaName = Schema.Name If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE SCHEMA: " & Schema.Name & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE SCHEMA ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(SchemaName, Context)) If Schema.HasProperty("Schema") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & "AUTHORIZATION " & Schema.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document Document.Write(vbNewLine) ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Schema.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON SCHEMA " & SchemaName & " IS '" & Schema.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document Document.Write(vbLf) End If End If ' End Generate Comments End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Schema Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Schema Set Schema = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Schema.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Schema.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Schema.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Schema.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP SCHEMA: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP SCHEMA IF EXISTS " ) Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Schema.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In Schema.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Schema.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER SCHEMA: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER SCHEMA " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next For Each ModifiedProperty In Schema.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If Schema.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SCHEMA: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SCHEMA " & ObjectName(Owner, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & Schema.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SCHEMA: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON SCHEMA " & ObjectName(Schema, Options) & " IS '" & Schema.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Index Script
Function index_option(Index, Options) Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim StorageParam If Index.HasProperty("Fill Factor") Then StorageParam = "(Fillfactor=" & Index.Property("Fill Factor").AsString & ")" End If If StorageParam <> "" Then index_option = index_option & vbNewLine & "WITH (" & StorageParam & ")" End If If Index.HasProperty("TABLESPACE") Then index_option = index_option & vbNewLine & "TABLESPACE = " & QuoteStrE(Index.Property("TABLESPACE").AsString, Context) End If Dim PrimarKeyIndex PrimarKeyIndex = False If Index.HasProperty("Key") Then Dim Key Set Key = Index.Property("Key").AsObject If Key.TypeName = "Key Constraint" Then If Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Primary" Then PrimarKeyIndex = True End If End If End If ' Allow Where only for non-primary key index If PrimarKeyIndex = False Then Dim WhereClause WhereClause = Index.Property("Where Filter Expression").AsString If WhereClause <> "" Then index_option = index_option & vbNewLine & "WHERE " & WhereClause End If End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Index Set Index = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options If Index.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If ' is it generated by a key? Dim Generate Generate = True If Index.HasProperty("Key") Then Dim Key Set Key = Index.Property("Key").AsObject If Key.TypeName = "Key Constraint" Then If Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Primary" And Options.Property("Generate PK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False ElseIf Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Unique" And Options.Property("Generate UK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If ElseIf Key.TypeName = "Relation" Then If Options.Property("Generate FK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If End If End If If Generate = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim IndexMembers Set IndexMembers = Index.Children("Index Member") If IndexMembers.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub End If If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE INDEX: " & Index.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE") If Index.Property("Unique").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" UNIQUE") End If Document.Write(" INDEX ") If Index.HasProperty("Concurrently") And Index.Property("Concurrently").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" CONCURRENTLY") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Index.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON ") Dim Table Set Table = Index.Owner() If Table.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & vbNewLine) If Index.HasProperty("Storage Type") Then Document.Write("USING " & Index.Property("Storage Type").AsString & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("(") Dim FirstMember FirstMember = True Dim IndexMember For Each IndexMember In IndexMembers If IndexMember.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If FirstMember = False Then Document.Write(",") Else FirstMember = False End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab) If IndexMember.HasProperty("Column") Then Dim Column Set Column = IndexMember.Property("Column").AsObject Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Column.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Else ' expression column Dim ExpressionValue ExpressionValue = IndexMember.Property("Expression Value").AsString If ExpressionValue <> "" Then Document.Write("(" & QuoteStrE(IndexMember.Property("Expression Value").AsString, Context) & ")") Else Document.Write("( /* TO DO: Provide an expression value... this will generate an error */ )") End If End If If IndexMember.HasProperty("Operator Class") Then Document.Write(" " & IndexMember.Property("Operator Class").AsString) End If If IndexMember.HasProperty("Sort Order") Then Document.Write(" " & IndexMember.Property("Sort Order").AsString) End If If IndexMember.HasProperty("Nulls First") Then If IndexMember.Property("Nulls First").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" NULLS FIRST") Else Document.Write(" NULLS LAST") End If End If End If Next Document.Write(vbNewLine & ")") Dim Clause Clause = index_option(Index, Options) If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & Clause) End If AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Index.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON INDEX ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Index.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" IS '" & Index.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Index Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Index Set Index = Context.Object Dim Generate Generate = True Dim HasKey HasKey = False Dim Key Dim ModifiedProperty For Each ModifiedProperty In Index.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Key" Then Key = Index.OriginalProperty("Key").AsObject HasKey = True Exit For End If Next If HasKey = True Or Index.HasProperty("Key") Then If HasKey = False Then Set Key = Index.Property("Key").AsObject End If If Key.TypeName = "Key Constraint" Then If Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Primary" And Options.Property("Generate PK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False ElseIf Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Unique" And Options.Property("Generate UK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If ElseIf Key.TypeName = "Relation" Then If Options.Property("Generate FK Index").AsBoolean = False Then Generate = False End If End If End If If Generate = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Index.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Index.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Index.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In Index.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Unique" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Index.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP INDEX : " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP INDEX IF EXISTS " ) Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Index.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In Index.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Index.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER INDEX: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Index.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER INDEX " & QuoteStrE(Index.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(Index.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER INDEX " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next For Each ModifiedProperty In Index.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "TABLESPACE" Then If Index.HasProperty("TABLESPACE") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER INDEX: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER INDEX " & ObjectName(Index, Options)) Document.Write(" SET TABLESPACE " & Index.Property("TABLESPACE").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Fill Factor" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER INDEX: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER INDEX " & ObjectName(Index, Options)) If Index.HasProperty("Fill Factor") Then Document.Write(" SET (Fillfactor=" & Index.Property("Fill Factor").AsString & ")") Else Document.Write(" RESET (Fillfactor)") End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER INDEX: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON INDEX " & ObjectName(Index, Options) & " IS '" & Index.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next
End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Details Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Foreign Key Constraint Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Relation Set Relation = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options If Relation.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If If Relation.HasProperty("Parent Table") = False Then Exit Sub End If If Relation.HasProperty("Parent Key") = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim FKMembers Set FKMembers = Relation.Children("FK Member") If FKMembers.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub End If Dim FKMember Dim ChildColumn Dim ParentColumn Dim AnyFKMembers AnyFKMembers = False For Each FKMember In FKMembers Set ChildColumn = FKMember.Property("Child Column").AsObject Set ParentColumn =
