FKMember.Property("Parent Column").AsObject If Not ChildColumn Is Nothing And Not ParentColumn Is Nothing Then If ChildColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean And ParentColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then AnyFKMembers = True Exit For End If End If Next If AnyFkMembers = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim ParentTable Set ParentTable = Relation.Property("Parent Table").AsObject If ParentTable.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim ParentKey Set ParentKey = Relation.Property("Parent Key").AsObject If ParentKey.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If If Options.Property("Generate FK Constraint Name").AsBoolean And Relation.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(Relation.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") End If Document.Write("FOREIGN KEY ") If Relation.HasProperty("Index") Then Dim Index Set Index = Relation.Property("Index").AsObject If Index.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(Index.Name & " ") End If End If Document.Write("(") Dim FirstMember FirstMember = True For Each FKMember In FKMembers Set ChildColumn = FKMember.Property("Child Column").AsObject Set ParentColumn = FKMember.Property("Parent Column").AsObject If ChildColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean And ParentColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If FirstMember = False Then Document.Write(", ") Else FirstMember = False End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ChildColumn.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) End If Next Document.Write(")" & vbNewLine & vbTab & vbTab & "REFERENCES ") If ParentTable.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ParentTable.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ParentTable.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" (") FirstMember = True For Each FKMember In FKMembers Set ParentColumn = FKMember.Property("Parent Column").AsObject If FirstMember = False Then Document.Write(", ") Else FirstMember = False End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ParentColumn.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Next Document.Write(")") If Relation.HasProperty("Match Type") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & vbTab & UCase(Relation.Property("Match Type").AsString)) End If If Relation.HasProperty("Delete Rule") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & vbTab & "ON DELETE " & UCase(Relation.Property("Delete Rule").AsString)) End If If Relation.HasProperty("Update Rule") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & vbTab & "ON UPDATE " & Ucase(Relation.Property("Update Rule").AsString)) End If Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(Relation) If State <> "" Then Clause = Clause & " " & State End If If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Foreign Key Constraint Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim FKKey Set FKKey = Context.Object If FKKey.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim Table Set Table = FKKey.Owner Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CreateDetails CreateDetails = FKKey.Evaluate("Details Script") If CreateDetails = "" Then Exit Sub End If If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE FOREIGN KEY CONSTRAINT: " & FKKey.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") Call OutputObjectName(Table, Document, Options) Document.Write(" ADD " & vbNewLine & vbTab) Document.Write(CreateDetails) AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If FKKey.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(FKKey.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(Table, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & FKKey.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter FK Constraint Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim FKConstraint Set FKConstraint = Context.Object ' Table Parent Changed.... Dim OldOwner Set OldOwner = FKConstraint.OldOwner Dim Owner Set Owner = FKConstraint.Owner Dim Table Set Table = FKConstraint.Owner If Owner.Name <> OldOwner.Name Then ' Drop and recreate the constraint Dim OldTableName Dim FKConstraintName Dim CreateStmt FKConstraintName = FKConstraint.Property("Name").AsString OldTableName = OldOwner.Name OriginalKeyConstraintName = FKConstraint.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString CurrentKeyConstraintName = FKConstraint.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP FOREIGN KEY: " & OldTableName & "." & OriginalKeyConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If OldOwner.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(OldOwner.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OldTableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(OldTableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(OriginalKeyConstraintName, Context) & ";" & vbNewLine) Document.Write(FKConstraint.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End If ' Pretty much on property change we need to drop & recreate Dim ModifiedProperty For Each ModifiedProperty In FKConstraint.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Match Type" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Delete Rule" Or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Update Rule" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Parent Table" Then TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString OriginalKeyConstraintName = FKConstraint.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString CurrentKeyConstraintName = FKConstraint.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP FOREIGN KEY: " & TableName & "." & OriginalKeyConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(OriginalKeyConstraintName, Context) & ";" & vbNewLine) Document.Write(FKConstraint.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End If Next CurrentName = FKConstraint.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CONSTRAINT COMMENT CHANGE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(FKConstraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(Table, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & FKConstraint.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Drop Constraint Script Function TopOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TopOwner = Nothing ElseIf Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" or Obj.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Set TopOwner = Obj Else Set TopOwner = TopOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If CurrentObject.TypeName = "Check Constraint" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Type").AsString = "NotNull" And CurrentObject.Owner.TypeName = "Column" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If End If End If Dim TopObject Set TopObject = TopOwner(CurrentObject) Dim TopObjectName TopObjectName = TopObject.Name ConstraintName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP CONSTRAINT: " & TopObjectName & "." & ConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If TopObject.TypeName = "Table" Or TopObject.TypeName = "Internal Table" Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") ElseIf TopObject.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN ") End If Document.Write(ObjectName(TopObject, Options)) Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & ObjectName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Trigger Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Trigger Set Trigger = Context.Object If Trigger.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = true Then Dim TriggerName TriggerName = Trigger.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE TRIGGER: " & TriggerName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Dim TriggerOwner Set TriggerOwner = Trigger.Owner Document.Write("CREATE TRIGGER ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TriggerName, Context) & vbNewLine) Dim TriggerType TriggerType = "After" If Trigger.HasProperty("Trigger Type") = True Then TriggerType = Trigger.Property("Trigger Type").AsString End If Document.Write(TriggerType) Document.Write(" " & Trigger.Property("Triggering Event").AsString) Document.Write(vbNewLine) Document.Write("ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options) & vbNewLine) Document.Write(Trigger.Property("Trigger Level").AsString & vbNewLine) Document.Write("EXECUTE PROCEDURE " & QuoteStrE(Trigger.Property("Function").AsString, Context) & "(") Dim Params Params = Trigger.Property("Parameters").AsString If Params <> "" Then Document.Write(Params) End If Document.Write(")") AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Trigger.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON TRIGGER " & ObjectName(Trigger, Options) & " ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options) & " IS '" & Trigger.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter Trigger Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Trigger Set Trigger = Context.Object Dim TriggerOwner Set TriggerOwner = Trigger.Owner Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Trigger.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Trigger.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Trigger.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In Trigger.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Trigger Type" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Triggering Event" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Trigger Level" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Called Function" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Trigger.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP TRIGGER: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TRIGGER IF EXISTS ") If Trigger.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Trigger.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write("ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options)) Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Trigger.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if For Each ModifiedProperty In Trigger.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TRIGGER: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TRIGGER " & CurrentName & " ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options) & " RENAME TO " & Trigger.Property("Name").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TRIGGER: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON TRIGGER " & ObjectName(Trigger, Options) & " ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options) & " IS '" & Trigger.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' PostgreSQL Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Set Options = Context.Options Set Trigger = Context.Object If Trigger.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then TriggerName = Trigger.Name If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP TRIGGER: " & TriggerName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TRIGGER IF EXISTS ") If Trigger.HasProperty("Schema") And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Trigger.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TriggerName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TriggerName, Context)) End If Set TriggerOwner = Trigger.Owner Document.Write("ON " & ObjectName(TriggerOwner, Options)) Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter View Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim View Set View = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = View.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In View.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = View.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true If NeedsRecreated = True Then If View.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP VIEW: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP VIEW IF EXISTS " ) If View.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(View.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(View.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if ' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In View.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = View.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER VIEW: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If View.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER VIEW " & QuoteStrE(View.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(View.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER VIEW " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next
For Each ModifiedProperty In View.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If View.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER VIEW: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & ObjectOriginalName(View, Options)) Document.Write(" SET SCHEMA " & View.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If View.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER VIEW: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & ObjectName(View, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & View.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER VIEW: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON VIEW " & ObjectName(View, Options) & " IS '" & View.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Create View Script
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim View Set View = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options
If Options.Property("Create Views").AsBoolean = False Or View.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If
Dim ViewName ViewName = View.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE VIEW: " & ViewName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Dim NeedSpace NeedSpace = False Document.Write("CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW ") Document.Write(ObjectName(View, Options) & vbNewLine) Document.Write("(") ' Columns Dim FirstRow FirstRow = True Dim Column For Each Column In View.Children("Column") If Column.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If FirstRow = False Then Document.Write(",") Else FirstRow = False End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab) Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Column.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) End If Next Document.Write(vbNewLine & ")")
Document.Write(" AS" & vbNewLine ) If View.Property("User Defined View").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(View.Property("User Defined View SQL").AsString & vbNewLine) Else ' Selects FirstRow = True Dim SelectElem For Each SelectElem In View.Children("Select") If SelectElem.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(SelectElem.Evaluate("Create Script") & vbNewLine) If SelectElem.HasProperty("Select Operator") Then Document.Write(SelectElem.Property("Select Operator").AsString & vbNewLine) End If End If Next End If AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If View.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON VIEW " & ObjectName(View, Options) & " IS '" & View.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments If View.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER TABLE " & ObjectName(View, Options) & " OWNER TO " & View.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Convert Datatype
script-properties.script.text:
' Convert to PostgreSQL Datatype Function DatatypeName(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then DatatypeName = Left(Datatype, Idx - 1) Else DatatypeName = Datatype End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam1(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Idx2 - Idx - 1) Else DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx - 1) End If Else DatatypeParam1 = -1 End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam2(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam2 = Mid(Datatype, Idx2 + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx2 - 1) Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Obj Set Obj = Context.Object Dim PrevDatabase PrevDatabase = Context.PrevDatabase Dim CurDatatype CurDatatype = Obj.Property("Datatype").AsString Dim CurName CurName = DatatypeName(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam1 CurParam1 = DatatypeParam1(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam2 CurParam2 = DatatypeParam2(CurDatatype) Dim NewDatatype NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Select Case PrevDatabase Case "MySQL 5.0", "MySQL 5.1", "MySQL 6.0" Select Case CurName Case "BIT", "BOOL", "BOOLEAN" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "TINYINT", "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "MEDIUMINT", "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "DEC", "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC", "FIXED" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "DATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "YEAR" NewDatatype = "date" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR", "CHARACTER VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR", "NATIONAL CHARACTER VARYING", "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "BINARY", "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bit varying" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "MEDIUMBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "LONGBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "TINYTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "TEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "MEDIUMTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "LONGTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "ENUM" NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Case "SET" NewDatatype = "varchar(100)" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "Oracle 8i", "Oracle 9i", "Oracle 10g", "Oracle 11g" Select Case CurName Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "NUMBER" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE", "TIMESTAMP WITH LOCAL TIME ZONE" NewDatatype = "timestamp with time zone" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR2", "CHARACTER VARYING", "CHAR VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "RAW" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "NCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the datatype get deleted - will inherit the default End Select Case "SQL Server 2000", "SQL Server 2005", "SQL Server 2008", "SQL Azure", "SQL Server Compact 3.5" Select Case CurName Case "bigint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "int" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "smallint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "tinyint" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "bit" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "decimal", "numeric" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "money" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "smallmoney" NewDatatype = "money" Case "float" NewDatatype = "real" Case "real" NewDatatype = "real" Case "datetime", "smalldatetime", "datetime2", "datetimeoffset" NewDatatype = "date" Case "timestamp" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "time" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "date" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "char" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "varchar" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "text", "ntext" NewDatatype = "text" Case "nchar" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "nvarchar" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "binary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "varbinary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "image" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "sql_variant" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "rowversion" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "uniqueidentifier" NewDatatype = "integer" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "ODBC", "Access 2003", "Access 2007", "Access 2010" Select Case CurName Case "BIT" NewDatatype = "boolean" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATETIME", "UTCDATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME", "UTCTIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "WCHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "BINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "GUID" NewDatatype = "char(128)" Case "UNKNOWN" NewDatatype = "" Case Else NewDatatype = "" End Select Case "DB2 LUW 7", "DB2 UDB 8", "DB2 LUW 9", "DB2 LUW 9.5", "DB2 LUW 9.7", "DB2 7 for z/OS", "DB2 8 for z/OS", "DB2 9 for z/OS" Select Case CurName Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "BLOB", "BINARY LARGE OBJECT" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CHAR", "CHARACTER" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If End If Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECFLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "INTEGER", "INT" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then If CurParam1 <= 8000 Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If End If End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If Case "GRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "LONG VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "DBCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DB2SECURITYLABEL" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "XML" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case Else Document.Write("Unknown Previous Database") Exit Sub End Select If NewDatatype <> "" Then Obj.SetDatatype(NewDatatype) End If Document.Write("Ok") End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Create Domain script
Function default_expr(Domain, Options) If Domain.Property("Default Expression").AsString <> "" Then default_expr = "DEFAULT " default_expr = default_expr & Domain.Property("Default Expression").AsString End If End Function
Function inline_constraint(Domain, Context) inline_constraint = "" For Each CheckConstraint In Domain.Children("Check Constraint") If CheckConstraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Clause = "CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(CheckConstraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " " End If Clause = Clause & "CHECK (" & CheckConstraint.Evaluate("Search Condition") & ")" Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(CheckConstraint) If State <> "" Then Clause = Clause & " " & State End If If Clause <> "" Then If inline_constraint <> "" Then inline_constraint = inline_constraint & " " End If inline_constraint = inline_constraint & Clause End If Next End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Domain Set Domain = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Clause Dim QualifiedName If Domain.HasLocalProperty("Generate") = False Or Domain.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If
Dim DomName DomName = Domain.Property("Name").AsString If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE DOMAIN: " & DomName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE DOMAIN ") If Domain.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then QualifiedName = QuoteStrE(Domain.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(DomName, Context) Else QualifiedName = QuoteStrE(DomName, Context) End If Document.Write(QualifiedName) Document.Write(" AS ") Dim DomType DomType = Domain.Property("Datatype").AsString Document.Write(DomType) Clause = default_expr(Domain, Options) If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If If Domain.Property("Not Null").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" NOT NULL") End If Clause = inline_constraint(Domain, Context) If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Domain.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON DOMAIN " & QualifiedName & " IS '" & Domain.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments If Domain.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER DOMAIN " & QualifiedName & " OWNER TO " & Domain.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Domain Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Domain Set Domain = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Domain.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Domain.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Domain.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In Domain.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Datatype" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next
If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Domain.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP DOMAIN: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP DOMAIN IF EXISTS " ) If Domain.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Domain.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Domain.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
For Each ModifiedProperty In Domain.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If Domain.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER DOMAIN: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN " & ObjectOriginalName(Domain, Options)) Document.Write(" SET SCHEMA " & Domain.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Not Null" Then If Domain.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER DOMAIN: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN " & ObjectName(Domain, Options)) If Domain.Property("Not Null").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" SET NOT NULL") Else Document.Write(" DROP NOT NULL") End If End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If Domain.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER DOMAIN: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN " & ObjectName(Domain, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & Domain.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER DOMAIN: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON DOMAIN " & ObjectName(Domain, Options) & " IS '" & Domain.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Column Domain Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP DOMAIN: " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP DOMAIN IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Convert Datatype
script-properties.script.text:
' Convert to PostgreSQL Datatype Function DatatypeName(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then DatatypeName = Left(Datatype, Idx - 1) Else DatatypeName = Datatype End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam1(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Idx2 - Idx - 1) Else DatatypeParam1 = Mid(Datatype, Idx + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx - 1) End If Else DatatypeParam1 = -1 End If End Function
Function DatatypeParam2(Datatype) Dim Idx Idx = InStr(Datatype, "(") If Idx > 0 Then Dim Idx2 Idx2 = InStr(Idx, Datatype, ",") If Idx2 > 0 Then DatatypeParam2 = Mid(Datatype, Idx2 + 1, Len(Datatype) - Idx2 - 1) Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If Else DatatypeParam2 = -1 End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Obj Set Obj = Context.Object Dim PrevDatabase PrevDatabase = Context.PrevDatabase Dim CurDatatype CurDatatype = Obj.Property("Datatype").AsString Dim CurName CurName = DatatypeName(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam1 CurParam1 = DatatypeParam1(CurDatatype) Dim CurParam2 CurParam2 = DatatypeParam2(CurDatatype) Dim NewDatatype NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Select Case PrevDatabase Case "MySQL 5.0", "MySQL 5.1", "MySQL 6.0" Select Case CurName Case "BIT", "BOOL", "BOOLEAN" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "TINYINT", "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "MEDIUMINT", "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "DEC", "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC", "FIXED" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "DATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "YEAR" NewDatatype = "date" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR", "CHARACTER VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR", "NATIONAL CHARACTER VARYING", "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "BINARY", "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bit varying" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "MEDIUMBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "LONGBLOB" NewDatatype = "bit varying" Case "TINYTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "TEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "MEDIUMTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "LONGTEXT" NewDatatype = "text" Case "ENUM" NewDatatype = "varchar(20)" Case "SET" NewDatatype = "varchar(100)" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "Oracle 8i", "Oracle 9i", "Oracle 10g", "Oracle 11g" Select Case CurName Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INT", "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "NUMBER" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE", "TIMESTAMP WITH LOCAL TIME ZONE" NewDatatype = "timestamp with time zone" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NCHAR", "NATIONAL CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR2", "CHARACTER VARYING", "CHAR VARYING" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "NVARCHAR2" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "RAW" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "BLOB" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "NCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the datatype get deleted - will inherit the default End Select Case "SQL Server 2000", "SQL Server 2005", "SQL Server 2008", "SQL Azure", "SQL Server Compact 3.5" Select Case CurName Case "bigint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "int" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "smallint" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "tinyint" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "bit" NewDatatype = "boolean" Case "decimal", "numeric" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "money" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "smallmoney" NewDatatype = "money" Case "float" NewDatatype = "real" Case "real" NewDatatype = "real" Case "datetime", "smalldatetime", "datetime2", "datetimeoffset" NewDatatype = "date" Case "timestamp" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "time" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "date" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "char" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "varchar" NewDatatype = CurDatatype Case "text", "ntext" NewDatatype = "text" Case "nchar" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "nvarchar" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "binary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "varbinary" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "image" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "sql_variant" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "rowversion" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "uniqueidentifier" NewDatatype = "integer" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case "ODBC", "Access 2003", "Access 2007", "Access 2010" Select Case CurName Case "BIT" NewDatatype = "boolean" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "TINYINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "INTEGER" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE", "DOUBLE PRECISION" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DATETIME", "UTCDATETIME" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "TIME", "UTCTIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "CHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "WCHAR" NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "BINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "GUID" NewDatatype = "char(128)" Case "UNKNOWN" NewDatatype = "" Case Else NewDatatype = "" End Select Case "DB2 LUW 7", "DB2 UDB 8", "DB2 LUW 9", "DB2 LUW 9.5", "DB2 LUW 9.7", "DB2 7 for z/OS", "DB2 8 for z/OS", "DB2 9 for z/OS" Select Case CurName Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "BLOB", "BINARY LARGE OBJECT" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CHAR", "CHARACTER" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If End If Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECFLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "INTEGER", "INT" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then If CurParam1 <= 8000 Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If End If End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If Case "GRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "LONG VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "DBCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DB2SECURITYLABEL" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "XML" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case Else Document.Write("Unknown Previous Database") Exit Sub End Select If NewDatatype <> "" Then Obj.SetDatatype(NewDatatype) End If Document.Write("Ok") End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Function Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim FunctionObj Set FunctionObj = Context.Object If FunctionObj.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then Dim FunctionName FunctionName = FunctionObj.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE FUNCTION: " & FunctionName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Dim FullFunctionName If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then FullFunctionName = QuoteStrE(FunctionObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(FunctionName, Context) Else FullFunctionName = QuoteStrE(FunctionName, Context) End If Document.Write("CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION " & FullFunctionName) Document.Write("(") First = True Set Params = FunctionObj.Children("Param") For Each Param In Params If First = True Then First = False Else Document.Write(", ") End If Document.Write(Param.Evaluate("Create Script")) Next Document.Write(")") Document.Write(vbNewLine) If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Return Code") Then Document.Write("RETURNS ") If FunctionObj.Property("Return As Set").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("SETOF ") End If Document.Write(FunctionObj.Property("Return Code").AsString & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("AS" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("$BODY$" & vbNewLine) Document.Write(FunctionObj.Property("Text").AsString & vbNewLine) Document.Write("$BODY$" & vbNewLine) If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Function Language") Then Document.Write("LANGUAGE '" & FunctionObj.Property("Function Language").AsString & "' ") End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Volatility") Then Document.Write(FunctionObj.Property("Volatility").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Called On Null Input") Then If FunctionObj.Property("Called On Null Input").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("CALLED ON NULL INPUT" & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write("RETURNS NULL ON NULL INPUT" & vbNewLine) End If End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Security Definer") Then If FunctionObj.Property("Security Definer").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("SECURITY DEFINER" & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write("SECURITY INVOKER" & vbNewLine) End If End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Cost") Then Document.Write("COST " & FunctionObj.Property("Cost").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Rows") Then Document.Write("ROWS " & FunctionObj.Property("Rows").AsString & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If FunctionObj.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON FUNCTION " & FullFunctionName & "(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ") IS '" & FunctionObj.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER FUNCTION " & FullFunctionName & "(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ") OWNER TO " & FunctionObj.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Function Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim FunctionObj Set FunctionObj = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = FunctionObj.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In FunctionObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = FunctionObj.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In FunctionObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Param Names" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Param Types" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Param Modes" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Return As Set" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next For Each ModifiedProperty In FunctionObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Return Code" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Text" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Function Language" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next
If NeedsRecreated = True Then If FunctionObj.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP FUNCTION: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS " ) If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(FunctionObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ") CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(FunctionObj.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In FunctionObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = FunctionObj.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & QuoteStrE(FunctionObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(FunctionObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next
For Each ModifiedProperty In FunctionObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & ObjectOriginalName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" SET SCHEMA " & FunctionObj.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Volatility" Then If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & ObjectName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(FunctionObj.Property("Volatility").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Cost" Then If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & ObjectName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" COST " & FunctionObj.Property("Cost").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Rows" Then If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & ObjectName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" ROWS " & FunctionObj.Property("Rows").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If FunctionObj.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER FUNCTION " & ObjectName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & FunctionObj.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER FUNCTION: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON FUNCTION " & ObjectName(FunctionObj, Options)) Document.Write("(" & FunctionObj.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ")") Document.Write(" IS '" & FunctionObj.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim ObjectName ObjectName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP FUNCTION: " & ObjectName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS ") If CurrentObject.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(CurrentObject.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(ObjectName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ObjectName, Context)) End If Document.Write("(" & CurrentObject.Property("Param Types List").AsString & ") CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Create Index Member Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim IndexMember Set IndexMember = Context.Object Dim ParentIndex Set ParentIndex = IndexMember.Owner Document.Write(ParentIndex.DropStatement) Document.Write(ParentIndex.CreateStatement) End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter Index Member Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim IndexMember Set IndexMember = Context.Object Dim ParentIndex Set ParentIndex = IndexMember.Owner Dim ModifiedProperty For Each ModifiedProperty In IndexMember.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Descending" Then Document.Write(ParentIndex.DropStatement) Document.Write(ParentIndex.CreateStatement) Exit For End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Create Tablespace Script
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Tablespace Set Tablespace = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options If Tablespace.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim TablespaceName TablespaceName = QuoteStrE(Tablespace.Property("Name").AsString, Context) If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE TABLESPACE: " & Tablespace.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE TABLESPACE ") Document.Write(TablespaceName) If TableSpace.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & "OWNER " & Tablespace.Property("Owner").AsString) End If If TableSpace.HasProperty("Tablespace Location") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & "LOCATION '" & Tablespace.Property("Tablespace Location").AsString & "'") End If Document.Write(vbNewLine) AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Tablespace.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON TABLESPACE " & TablespaceName & " IS '" & Tablespace.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Tablespace Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Tablespace Set Tablespace = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Tablespace.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Tablespace.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Tablespace.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In Tablespace.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Tablespace Location" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next
If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Tablespace.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP TABLESPACE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TABLESPACE IF EXISTS " ) If Tablespace.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Tablespace.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Tablespace.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In Tablespace.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Tablespace.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER TABLESPACE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER TABLESPACE " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next
For Each ModifiedProperty In Tablespace.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If Tablespace.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TABLESPACE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TABLESPACE " & ObjectName(Tablespace, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & Tablespace.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TABLESPACE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON TABLESPACE " & ObjectName(Tablespace, Options) & " IS '" & Tablespace.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim ObjectName ObjectName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP TABLESPACE: " & ObjectName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TABLESPACE IF EXISTS ") If CurrentObject.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(CurrentObject.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(ObjectName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(ObjectName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Create View Select Script Function ExpressionValue(Expression, Options) ExpressionValue = Expression.Property("SQL DDL").AsString End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim ViewSelect Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Set ViewSelect = Context.Object If ViewSelect.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("SELECT") If ViewSelect.HasProperty("Distinct") = True Then If ViewSelect.Property("Distinct").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(" DISTINCT") Else Document.Write(" ALL") End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine) Dim FirstRow FirstRow = True ' Select Expressions If ViewSelect.Property("Select Is Star").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(vbTab & "*") Else Dim Expression For Each Expression In ViewSelect.Children("Expression Column") If FirstRow = False Then Document.Write("," & vbNewLine) Else FirstRow = False End If If Expression.HasLocalProperty("Name") Then Document.Write(vbTab & ExpressionValue(Expression, Options) & " AS """ & Expression.Property("Name").AsString & """") Else Document.Write(vbTab & ExpressionValue(Expression, Options)) End If Next End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & "FROM" & vbNewLine) FirstRow = True ' From Tables Dim FromTable For Each FromTable In ViewSelect.Children("Select From") If FirstRow = False Then Document.Write("," & vbNewLine) Else FirstRow = False End If Dim ParentTableObj Set ParentTableObj = FromTable.Property("Parent Table").AsObject If Not ParentTableObj Is Nothing Then If FromTable.Property("System Generated Name").AsBoolean = False Then Document.Write(vbTab & ObjectName(ParentTableObj, Options) & " " & QuoteStrE(FromTable.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Else Document.Write(vbTab & ObjectName(ParentTableObj, Options)) End If Else Document.Write(vbTab & FromTable.Property("Parent Table Name").AsString) End If Next ' Should be just one such child For Each Clause In ViewSelect.Children("Where") Document.Write(vbNewLine & "WHERE" & vbTab & ExpressionValue(Clause, Options)) Next ' Should be just one such child For Each Clause In ViewSelect.Children("Group By") Document.Write(vbNewLine & "GROUP BY" & vbTab & ExpressionValue(Clause, Options)) Next ' Should be just one such child For Each Clause In ViewSelect.Children("Having") Document.Write(vbNewLine & "HAVING" & vbTab & ExpressionValue(Clause, Options)) Next ' Should be just one such child For Each Clause In ViewSelect.Children("Order By") Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ORDER BY" & vbTab & ExpressionValue(Clause, Options)) Next End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Valid Values List Script Function SingleQuoteStr(Str, Quote) If Quote Then SingleQuoteStr = "'" & Str & "'" Else SingleQuoteStr = Str End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim ValidValuesList Set ValidValuesList = Context.Object
Dim ValidValues Dim ValidValue Dim First First = True Dim QuoteValues QuoteValues = False If ValidValuesList.HasProperty("Quote Values") Then QuoteValues = ValidValuesList.Property("Quote Values").AsBoolean End If Set ValidValues = ValidValuesList.Children("Valid Value") For Each ValidValue In ValidValues If First Then First = False Document.Write("IN (") Else Document.Write(", ") End If
Document.Write(SingleQuoteStr(ValidValue.Property("Name").AsString, QuoteValues)) Next If First = False Then Document.Write(")") End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Search Condition
script-properties.script.text: ' Column/Table Check Constraint Search Condition Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Constraint Set Constraint = Context.Object Dim ConstraintType ConstraintType = Constraint.Property("Type").AsString Dim Owner Set Owner = Constraint.Owner Select Case ConstraintType Case "Expression" Dim Expression For Each Expression In Constraint.Children("Table Based Expression") Document.Write(Expression.Property("SQL DDL").AsString) Next Case "Script" Document.Write("Overwrite this script to do something else...") Case "MinMax" Dim MinSet MinSet = False Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Owner.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") If Constraint.HasProperty("Min Value") Then MinSet = True Document.Write(Constraint.Property("Min Condition").AsString & " " & Constraint.Property("Min Value").AsString) End If If Constraint.HasProperty("Max Value") Then If MinSet Then Document.Write(" AND " & QuoteStrE(Owner.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") End If Document.Write(Constraint.Property("Max Condition").AsString & " " & Constraint.Property("Max Value").AsString) End If Case "ValidValues" Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Owner.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") If Constraint.HasProperty("Valid Values") Then Dim ValidValueList Set ValidValueList = Constraint.Property("Valid Values").AsObject Document.Write(ValidValueList.Evaluate("Create Script")) End If Case "NotNull" Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Owner.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" IS NOT NULL") End Select End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Check Constraint Script Function TopOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TopOwner = Nothing ElseIf Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" or Obj.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Set TopOwner = Obj Else Set TopOwner = TopOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Constraint Set Constraint = Context.Object If Constraint.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then ' Generate Not Null only if the name can be generated... If Constraint.Property("Type").AsString = "NotNull" And Constraint.Owner.TypeName = "Column" Then If Constraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If End If If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE CHECK CONSTRAINT: " & Constraint.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Dim TopObject Set TopObject = TopOwner(Constraint) Dim TopObjectName TopObjectName = TopObject.Name If TopObject.TypeName = "Table" Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") ElseIf TopObject.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN ") End If If TopObject.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TopObject.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TopObjectName, Context) & " ADD ") If Constraint.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(Constraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") End If Document.Write("CHECK (" & Constraint.Evaluate("Search Condition") & ")") Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(Constraint) If State <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & State) End If AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Constraint.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Constraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(TopObject, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & Constraint.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
Function TopOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TopOwner = Nothing ElseIf Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" or Obj.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Set TopOwner = Obj Else Set TopOwner = TopOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim CheckConstraint Set CheckConstraint = Context.Object Dim Table Set Table = TopOwner(CheckConstraint) TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString Dim ModifiedProperty Dim ModifedProps Set ModifedProps = CheckConstraint.ModifiedProperties For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString OriginalCheckConstraintName = CheckConstraint.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP CONSTRAINT: " & TableName & "." & OriginalCheckConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(OriginalCheckConstraintName, Context)) AddDelim Options, Document Document.Write(CheckConstraint.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End If Next CurrentName = CheckConstraint.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CONSTRAINT COMMENT CHANGE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(CheckConstraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(Table, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & CheckConstraint.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

' PostgreSQL Drop Constraint Script Function TopOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TopOwner = Nothing ElseIf Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" or Obj.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Set TopOwner = Obj Else Set TopOwner = TopOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If CurrentObject.TypeName = "Check Constraint" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Type").AsString = "NotNull" And CurrentObject.Owner.TypeName = "Column" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If End If End If Dim TopObject Set TopObject = TopOwner(CurrentObject) Dim TopObjectName TopObjectName = TopObject.Name ConstraintName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP CONSTRAINT: " & TopObjectName & "." & ConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If TopObject.TypeName = "Table" Or TopObject.TypeName = "Internal Table" Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") ElseIf TopObject.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN ") End If Document.Write(ObjectName(TopObject, Options)) Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & ObjectName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub
