script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Create Type Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Set TypeObj = Context.Object Set Options = Context.Options If TypeObj.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Or TypeObj.HasProperty("Type") = False Or TypeObj.Property("Type").AsString = "Scaler" Or TypeObj.Property("Type").AsString = "Alias" Then Exit Sub End If TypeType = TypeObj.Property("Type").AsString TypeNameS = TypeObj.Property("Name").AsString If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE TYPE: " & TypeNameS & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If
Document.Write("CREATE TYPE ") If TypeObj.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then QualifiedTypeName = QuoteStrE(TypeObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." End If QualifiedTypeName = QualifiedTypeName & QuoteStrE(TypeNameS, Context) Document.Write(QualifiedTypeName) Select Case TypeType Case "Object" Document.Write(" AS" & vbNewLine & "(") FirstAtt = True ' Attributes For Each Attribute In TypeObj.Children("Attribute") If Attribute.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If FirstAtt Then FirstAtt = False Else Document.Write(",") End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & Attribute.CreateStatement) End If Next Document.Write(vbNewLine & ")" & vbNewLine) Case "Enum" Document.Write(" AS ENUM" & vbNewLine & "(") FirstVal = True For Each EnumValueProp In TypeObj.Property("Enum Values").AsVector If FirstVal Then FirstVal = False Else Document.Write(",") End If Document.Write(vbNewLine & vbTab & "'" & EnumValueProp.AsString & "'") Next Document.Write(vbNewLine & ")" & vbNewLine) Case "External" Document.Write(vbNewLine & "(") Clause = "" If TypeObj.HasProperty("Input Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "INPUT = " & TypeObj.Property("Input Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Output Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "OUTPUT = " & TypeObj.Property("Output Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Receive Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "RECEIVE = " & TypeObj.Property("Receive Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Send Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "SEND = " & TypeObj.Property("Send Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Type Mod In Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "TYPMOD_IN =" & TypeObj.Property("Type Mod In Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Type Mod Out Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "TYPMOD_OUT =" & TypeObj.Property("Type Mod Out Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Analyze Function") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "ANALYZE =" & TypeObj.Property("Analyze Function").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Internal Length") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "INTERNALLENGTH = " If TypeObj.Property("Internal Length").AsString = "-1" Then Clause = Clause & "VARIABLE" Else Clause = Clause & TypeObj.Property("Internal Length").AsString End If End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Passed By Value") And TypeObj.Property("Passed By Value").AsBoolean Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "PASSEDBYVALUE" End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Alignment") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "ALIGNMENT = " & TypeObj.Property("Alignment").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Storage") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "STORAGE = " & TypeObj.Property("Storage").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Default") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "DEFAULT = " & TypeObj.Property("Default").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Element") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "ELEMENT=" & TypeObj.Property("Element").AsString End If If TypeObj.HasProperty("Delimiter") Then If Clause <> "" Then Clause = Clause & "," End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & vbTab & "DELIMITER = '" & TypeObj.Property("Delimiter").AsString & "'" End If Clause = Clause & vbNewLine & ")" & vbNewLine Document.write(Clause) End Select AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If TypeObj.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON TYPE " & QualifiedTypeName & " IS '" & TypeObj.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments If TypeObj.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER TYPE " & QualifiedTypeName & " OWNER TO " & TypeObj.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Type Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim TypeObj Set TypeObj = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = TypeObj.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In TypeObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = TypeObj.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In TypeObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Type" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next
If NeedsRecreated = True Then If TypeObj.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP TYPE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP TYPE IF EXISTS " ) If TypeObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(TypeObj.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(TypeObj.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
For Each ModifiedProperty In TypeObj.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If TypeObj.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TYPE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TYPE " & ObjectOriginalName(TypeObj, Options)) Document.Write(" SET SCHEMA " & TypeObj.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If TypeObj.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TYPE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER TYPE " & ObjectName(TypeObj, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & TypeObj.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER TYPE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON TYPE " & ObjectName(TypeObj, Options) & " IS '" & TypeObj.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Details Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Key Script
Function index_option(Index, Options) Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim StorageParam If Index.HasProperty("Fill Factor") Then StorageParam = "(Fillfactor=" & Index.Property("Fill Factor").AsString & ")" End If If StorageParam <> "" Then index_option = index_option & vbNewLine & "WITH (" & StorageParam & ")" End If If Index.HasProperty("TABLESPACE") Then index_option = index_option & vbNewLine & "USING INDEX TABLESPACE = " & QuoteStrE(Index.Property("TABLESPACE").AsString, Context) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Key Set Key = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim FirstMember Dim KeyColumnProp Dim KeyColumn Dim Table Set Table = Key.Owner() If Key.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = False Or Key.HasProperty("Columns") = False Then Exit Sub End If Dim AnyColumns AnyColumns = False For Each KeyColumnProp in Key.Property("Columns").AsVector Set KeyColumn = KeyColumnProp.AsObject If KeyColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then AnyColumns = True Exit For End If Next If AnyColumns = False Then Exit Sub End If If Key.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then If Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Unique" and Options.Property("Generate UK Constraint Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(Key.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") End If If Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Primary" and Options.Property("Generate PK Constraint Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(Key.Property("Name").AsString, Context) & " ") End If End If If (Key.Property("Type").AsString = "Primary") Then Document.Write("PRIMARY KEY (") Else Document.Write("UNIQUE (") End If FirstMember = True For Each KeyColumnProp in Key.Property("Columns").AsVector Set KeyColumn = KeyColumnProp.AsObject If KeyColumn.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then If FirstMember = False Then Document.Write(", ") Else FirstMember = False End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(KeyColumn.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) End If Next Document.Write(")") If Key.HasProperty("Index") Then Dim Index Set Index = Key.Property("Index").AsObject Dim IndexParameters IndexParameters = index_option(Index, Options) If IndexParameters <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & IndexParameters) End If End If Dim State State = PostgresqlConstraintState(Key) If State <> "" Then Clause = Clause & " " & State End If If Clause <> "" Then Document.Write(" " & Clause) End If
End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Key Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Key Set Key = Context.Object Dim Table Set Table = Key.Owner() Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CreateDetails CreateDetails = Key.Evaluate("Details Script") If CreateDetails = "" Then Exit Sub End If If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE KEY CONSTRAINT: " & Key.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") Call OutputObjectName(Table, Document, Options) Document.Write(" ADD " & vbNewLine & vbTab) Document.Write(CreateDetails) AddDelim Options, Document If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Key.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Key.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(Table, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & Key.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter Key Constraint Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim KeyConstraint Set KeyConstraint = Context.Object Dim Table Set Table = KeyConstraint.Owner Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim ModifiedProperty Dim ModifedProps Set ModifedProps = KeyConstraint.ModifiedProperties For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Columns" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Type" Then TableName = Table.Property("Name").AsString OriginalKeyConstraintName = KeyConstraint.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString CurrentKeyConstraintName = KeyConstraint.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP KEY: " & TableName & "." & OriginalKeyConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Table.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(Table.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER TABLE " & QuoteStrE(TableName, Context)) End If Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & QuoteStrE(OriginalKeyConstraintName, Context) & ";" & vbNewLine) Document.Write(KeyConstraint.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End If Next CurrentName = KeyConstraint.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In ModifedProps If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CONSTRAINT COMMENT CHANGE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("COMMENT ON CONSTRAINT ") Document.Write(QuoteStrE(KeyConstraint.Property("Name").AsString, Context)) Document.Write(" ON " & ObjectName(Table, Options)) Document.Write(" IS '" & KeyConstraint.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text:
' PostgreSQL Drop Constraint Script Function TopOwner(Obj) If Obj Is Nothing Then Set TopOwner = Nothing ElseIf Obj.TypeName = "Table" Or Obj.TypeName = "Internal Table" or Obj.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Set TopOwner = Obj Else Set TopOwner = TopOwner(Obj.Owner) End If End Function
Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If CurrentObject.TypeName = "Check Constraint" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Type").AsString = "NotNull" And CurrentObject.Owner.TypeName = "Column" Then If CurrentObject.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean = False Then Exit Sub End If End If End If Dim TopObject Set TopObject = TopOwner(CurrentObject) Dim TopObjectName TopObjectName = TopObject.Name ConstraintName = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP CONSTRAINT: " & TopObjectName & "." & ConstraintName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If TopObject.TypeName = "Table" Or TopObject.TypeName = "Internal Table" Then Document.Write("ALTER TABLE ") ElseIf TopObject.TypeName = "Column Domain" Then Document.Write("ALTER DOMAIN ") End If Document.Write(ObjectName(TopObject, Options)) Document.Write(" DROP CONSTRAINT " & ObjectName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARWCHAR" NewDatatype = "text" Case "BINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If Case "LONG VARBINARY" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "GUID" NewDatatype = "char(128)" Case "UNKNOWN" NewDatatype = "" Case Else NewDatatype = "" End Select Case "DB2 LUW 7", "DB2 UDB 8", "DB2 LUW 9", "DB2 LUW 9.5", "DB2 LUW 9.7", "DB2 7 for z/OS", "DB2 8 for z/OS", "DB2 9 for z/OS" Select Case CurName Case "BIGINT" NewDatatype = "bigint" Case "BLOB", "BINARY LARGE OBJECT" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "CHAR", "CHARACTER" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "char" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" End If End If Case "CLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DATE" NewDatatype = "date" Case "DECIMAL" NewDatatype = "decimal" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "NUMERIC" NewDatatype = "numeric" If CurParam1 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 If CurParam2 <> "" Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "," & CurParam2 End If NewDatatype = NewDatatype & ")" End If Case "DECFLOAT" NewDatatype = "real" Case "DOUBLE" NewDatatype = "double precision" Case "FLOAT" NewDatatype = "float" Case "INTEGER", "INT" NewDatatype = "integer" Case "SMALLINT" NewDatatype = "smallint" Case "REAL" NewDatatype = "real" Case "TIME" NewDatatype = "time" Case "TIMESTAMP" NewDatatype = "timestamp" Case "VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "varchar" If CurParam1 <> "" Then If CurParam1 <= 8000 Then NewDatatype = NewDatatype & "(" & CurParam1 & ")" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If End If End If Case "LONG VARCHAR" If Obj.HasProperty("For Data") And Obj.Property("For Data").AsString = "BIT" Then NewDatatype = "bytea" Else NewDatatype = "text" End If Case "GRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "LONG VARGRAPHIC" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "DBCLOB" NewDatatype = "text" Case "DB2SECURITYLABEL" NewDatatype = "bytea" Case "XML" NewDatatype = "text" Case Else NewDatatype = "" ' let the system warn when the datatype is deleted and inherit the default End Select Case Else Document.Write("Unknown Previous Database") Exit Sub End Select If NewDatatype <> "" Then Obj.SetDatatype(NewDatatype) End If Document.Write("Ok") End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Sequence Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Sequence Set Sequence = Context.Object If Sequence.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then Dim SequenceName SequenceName = Sequence.Property("Name").AsString If Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- CREATE SEQUENCE: " & SequenceName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE SEQUENCE ") If Sequence.HasProperty("Schema") And Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Sequence.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(SequenceName, Context) & vbNewLine) If Sequence.HasProperty("Increment By") Then Document.Write(vbTab & "INCREMENT BY " & Sequence.Property("Increment By").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Min Value") Then Document.Write(vbTab) If Sequence.Property("Min Value").AsString <> "NO MINVALUE" Then Document.Write("MINVALUE ") End If Document.Write(Sequence.Property("Min Value").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Max Value") Then Document.Write(vbTab) If Sequence.Property("Max Value").AsString <> "NO MAXVALUE" Then Document.Write("MAXVALUE ") End If Document.Write(Sequence.Property("Max Value").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Last Number") Then Document.Write(vbTab & "START " & Sequence.Property("Last Number").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Cache") Then Document.Write(vbTab & "CACHE " & Sequence.Property("Cache").AsString & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Cycle") Then If Sequence.Property("Cycle").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(vbTab & "CYCLE" & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(vbTab & "NO CYCLE" & vbNewLine) End If End If AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Sequence.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options) & " IS '" & Sequence.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments If Sequence.HasProperty("Owner") Then Document.Write(vbNewLine & "ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options) & " OWNER TO " & Sequence.Property("Owner").AsString) AddDelim Options, Document End If End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text:
' Alter Sequence Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Sequence Set Sequence = Context.Object Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Sequence.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Sequence.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Sequence.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Sequence.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP SEQUENCE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP SEQUENCE IF EXISTS " ) Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Sequence.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if
' Generate Name first For Each ModifiedProperty In Sequence.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Sequence.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If If Sequence.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & QuoteStrE(Sequence.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(Sequence.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) Else Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Document.Write(" RENAME TO " & QuoteStrE(CurrentName, Context)) End If AddDelim Options, Document Exit For End If Next For Each ModifiedProperty In Sequence.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Schema" Then If Sequence.HasProperty("Schema") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectOriginalName(Sequence, Options)) Document.Write(" SET SCHEMA " & Sequence.Property("Schema").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Min Value" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.HasProperty("Min Value") Then Document.Write(" MINVALUE " & Sequence.Property("Min Value").AsString & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(" NO MINVALUE") End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Max Value" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.HasProperty("Max Value") Then Document.Write(" MAXVALUE " & Sequence.Property("Max Value").AsString & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(" NO MAXVALUE") End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Increment By" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.HasProperty("Increment By") Then Document.Write(" INCREMENT BY " & Sequence.Property("Increment By").AsString & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Last Number" Then If Sequence.HasProperty("Last Number") Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) Document.Write(" RESTART WITH " & Sequence.Property("Last Number").AsString & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Cache Value" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.HasProperty("Cache Value") Then Document.Write(" CACHE " & Sequence.Property("Cache Value").AsString & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(" NO CACHE" & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Cycle Flag" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.Property("Cycle Flag").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" CYCLE" & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(" NO CYCLE" & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owned By" Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) If Sequence.HasProperty("Owned By") Then Dim Column Set Column = Sequence.Property("Owned By").AsObject Dim Table Set Table = Column.Owner Document.Write(" OWNED BY " & Table.Property("Name").AsString & "." & Column.Property("Name").AsString & vbNewLine) Else Document.Write(" OWNED BY NONE" & vbNewLine) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Owner" Then If Sequence.HasProperty("Owner") = True Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("ALTER SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options)) Document.Write(" OWNER TO " & Sequence.Property("Owner").AsString) End If AddDelim Options, Document ElseIf ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER SEQUENCE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON SEQUENCE " & ObjectName(Sequence, Options) & " IS '" & Sequence.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Object Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim CurrentObject Set CurrentObject = Context.Object If CurrentObject.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then Dim Name Name = CurrentObject.Property("Name").AsString Dim TypeName TypeName = CurrentObject.TypeName If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP " & TypeName & ": " & Name & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP " & UCase(TypeName) & " IF EXISTS " & ObjectOriginalName(CurrentObject, Options) & " CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Rule Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Rule Set Rule = Context.Object If Rule.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then Dim RuleName RuleName = Rule.Property("Name").AsString If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- CREATE RULE: " & RuleName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("CREATE OR REPLACE RULE ") If Rule.HasProperty("Schema") And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Rule.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & ".") End If Document.Write(QuoteStrE(RuleName, Context) & vbNewLine) Document.Write("AS ON " & Rule.Property("Event").AsString) Dim RuleOwner Set RuleOwner = Rule.Owner Document.Write(" TO " & ObjectName(RuleOwner, Options) & vbNewLine) If Rule.HasProperty("Where Condition") Then Document.Write("WHERE " & Rule.Property("Where Condition").AsString) End If Document.Write(vbNewLine) Document.Write("DO ") If Rule.HasProperty("Instead") Then If Rule.Property("Instead").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("INSTEAD") Else Document.write("ALSO") End If End If Document.Write(vbNewLine) If Rule.HasProperty("Command") Then Document.Write(Rule.Property("Command").AsString) Else Document.Write(vbTab & "NOTHING") End If Document.Write(vbNewLine) AddDelim Options, Document ' Generate Comments If Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then If Rule.Property("Comment").AsString <> "" Then Document.Write("COMMENT ON RULE " & ObjectName(Rule, Options) & " ON " & ObjectName(RuleOwner, Options) & " IS '" & Rule.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If End If ' End Generate Comments End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Alter Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Alter Rule Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Dim Context Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Dim Document Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Dim Rule Set Rule = Context.Object Dim RuleOwner Set RuleOwner = Rule.Owner Dim Options Set Options = Context.Options Dim OriginalName Dim CurrentName Dim ModifiedProperty Dim NeedsRecreated NeedsRecreated = False CurrentName = Rule.Property("Name").AsString For Each ModifiedProperty In Rule.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" Then OriginalName = Rule.OriginalProperty("Name").AsString Exit For End If Next ' Here we should first look for props that triggers a recreate and make NeedsRecreated true For Each ModifiedProperty In Rule.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Name" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Event" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Instead" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Where Condition" or ModifiedProperty.Name = "Command" Then NeedsRecreated = True Exit For End If Next If NeedsRecreated = True Then If Rule.Property("Generate").AsBoolean = True Then If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write("---" & vbNewLine & "--- DROP RULE: " & OriginalName & vbNewLine & "---" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP RULE IF EXISTS ") If Rule.HasProperty("Schema") = True And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean = True Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Rule.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(OriginalName, Context)) End If Document.Write("ON " & ObjectName(RuleOwner, Options)) Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If Document.Write(Rule.CreateStatement) Exit Sub End if For Each ModifiedProperty In Rule.ModifiedProperties If ModifiedProperty.Name = "Comment" And Options.Property("Generate Comments").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("-- ALTER RULE: " & CurrentName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) Document.Write("COMMENT ON RULE " & ObjectName(Rule, Options) & " ON " & ObjectName(RuleOwner, Options) & " IS '" & Rule.Property("Escaped Comment").AsString & "'") AddDelim Options, Document End If Next End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Drop Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Drop Rule Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Set Options = Context.Options Set Rule = Context.Object If Rule.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then RuleName = Rule.Name If Context.Options.Property("Generate Headers").AsBoolean Then Document.Write("--" & vbNewLine & "-- DROP RULE: " & RuleName & vbNewLine & "--" & vbNewLine) End If Document.Write("DROP RULE IF EXISTS ") If Rule.HasProperty("Schema") And Context.Options.Property("Generate Schema Names").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(QuoteStrE(Rule.Property("Schema").AsString, Context) & "." & QuoteStrE(RuleName, Context)) Else Document.Write(QuoteStrE(RuleName, Context)) End If Set RuleOwner = Rule.Owner Document.Write("ON " & ObjectName(RuleOwner, Options)) Document.Write(" CASCADE") AddDelim Options, Document End If End Sub

script-properties.script.name: Create Script
script-properties.script.text: ' Function Param Script Sub Evaluate_OnLoad() Set Context = CreateObject("SCF.ScriptContext") Set Options = Context.Options Set Document = Context.ScriptDocument Set FunctionParam = Context.Object If Not FunctionParam.Property("Generate").AsBoolean Then Exit Sub End If Document.Write(FunctionParam.Property("Mode").AsString) If FunctionParam.Property("Generate Name").AsBoolean Then Document.Write(" " & FunctionParam.Name) End If Document.Write(" " & FunctionParam.Property("Datatype").AsString) If FunctionParam.HasProperty("Default Expression") Then Document.write(" = " & FunctionParam.Property("Default Expression").AsString) End If End Sub
